<div class="main">

  <div class="main_view">
    <%= image_tag "top.jpg", :size =>'1665x830'%>
    <p>人々を幸せに。</p>
  </div>

  <div class="main_text">
    <p>デザインを武器に幸せな暮らしづくり</p>
    <p>社会貢献で快適を広くとどけたい</p>
  </div>

</div>


<div class="media">
  <div class="title_bar">
    <h1>メディア</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="posts">
      <% @tweets.each do |tweet|%>
      <div class="post">
        <div class="media_image">  
          <%= image_tag tweet.image.variant(resize: '200x200') if tweet.image.attached? %>
        </div>
        <div class="media_title">
          <%= tweet.title %>
        </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>    
  </div>
</div>